item.dc:creator: @Ii_1337_iI Ii 1337 iI
item.description:
@Ii_1337_iI wrote:

Go to Player.java and search “unique” you should see something like “giving the player a unique look” and under that are some Item ID’s just change them to the item you want. read what comes before it to know what spot it is.
